title: Ground News - Polish power and precision: Iga dominates Perth opener
text:
Summary by Ground News World No.1 Iga Swiatek has sent an ominous warning to her Australian Open competition with a comprehensive and classy straight-sets win over Brazil's Beatriz Haddad Maia. The four-time Grand Slam champion was a class above the world No.11. Share menu More
